        .about.lineUp
            span.annotated(style="width:75%;margin:auto") >. About Me<span class='cursor'>|</span>
            .cardHolderDiv
                .aboutCards
                    p.
                        Hi, Lara here! I am a <span style='color:#63fdd9'>software engineer</span> and a 
                        <span style='color:#63fdd9'>computer engineer</span>, on a quest to digitally
                        revolutionize the world! A warm welcome to you, dear visitor.
                .aboutCards
                    p.
                        I'm currently an undergrad student at 
                        <span style='color:#63fdd9'>Prince Mohammed Bin Fahd University, Saudi Arabia</span>. 
                        I'm majoring in both Software Engineering as well as Computer Engineering</strong>.
                .aboutCards
                    p.
                        My interests include <span style='color:#63fdd9'>Robotics</span>, 
                        <span style='color:#63fdd9'>Cloud Computing</span> and 
                        <span style='color:#63fdd9'>Artificial Intelligence</span>.
                        
                .aboutCards
                    p.
                        Did I tell you I really like <span style='color:#63fdd9'>psychology</span>? 
                        I attended a Pyschology summer course at <span style='color:#63fdd9'>Harvard</span>.
                        I also love <span style='color:#63fdd9'>swimming</span>! 
                        Helps me relax in the daily hustle and bustle of life.

        .skills.lineUp
            span.annotated(style="width:75%;margin:auto") >. Skills<span class='cursor'>|</span>
            .cardHolderDiv
                .skillCard
                    img(src="/Images/robot_head.png" width:20px)
                    .skillText
                        h1 Electronics and IoT
                        p.
                            I have extensive experience working with 
                            <span style='color:#63fdd9'>Arduino</span> and 
                            <span style='color:#63fdd9'>Raspberri Pi</span>. 
                            My most notable projects in this field are the 
                            <span style='color:#63fdd9'>Haptic VR glove</span> and 
                            <span style='color:#63fdd9'>Electronic Xylophone</span>.

                .skillCard
                    img(src="/Images/tag.png" width:20px)
                    .skillText
                        h1 Flask, HTML, CSS and JS
                        p.
                            I mainly focus on <span style='color:#63fdd9'>Front End Development</span>. 
                            My most notable projects in this field are the
                            <span style='color:#63fdd9'>Inventory Management System</span> and 
                            <span style='color:#63fdd9'>Gym Services Management</span> applications.
                .skillCard
                    img(src="/Images/3dPrinting.png" width:20px)
                    .skillText
                        h1 3D Modeling
                        p.
                            My 3D modeling skills come in handy for rapid prototyping 
                            as well as for building full fledged products. I'm well versed in
                            <span style='color:#63fdd9'>TinkerCad, Fusion360 and AutoCad</span>.
                .skillCard
                    img(src="/Images/programming.png" width:20px)
                    .skillText
                        h1 Java, Python
                        p.
                            I'm quite comfortable working with 
                            <span style='color:#63fdd9'>Java</span> and <span style='color:#63fdd9'>Python</span>. 
                            By extension, I am able to participate in projects 
                            that use frameworks built around the aforementioned languages.


        .projects.lineUp
            span.annotated(style="width:75%;margin:auto") >. Projects<span class='cursor'>|</span>
            .cardHolderDiv
                .projectCard(style="background-image:url('/Images/haptic.png')")
                    .projectText
                        h1 Haptic VR Glove
                        br
                        p.
                            A glove was constructed using IMUs and flex sensors which collected hand movement data. 
                            The data was fed to a Unity environment, where a virtual hand reflects the hand 
                            movement data collected from the glove. 
                            Events in the game result in haptic feedback on the glove.
                        p(style="color:red") Tools Used: Arduino, Unity
                .projectCard(style="background-image:url('/Images/ims.jpg')")
                    .projectText
                        h1 Inventory Management System
                        br
                        p.
                            Items are recognized by a raspberry pi through live video feed from a webcam. Users 
                            can check-in and check-out items. Inventory database is updated accordingly. 
                            Inventory, stock, check-outs and user information is displayed on a web application. 
                            New items can be registered by an admin using the 'Register Item' feature. 
                            Images of new items are captured which are used to retrain the deep learning model. 
                            Designed a 3D printed wall mounting case for the system using Fusion360.
                        p(style="color:red") Tools Used: Keras, OpenCV, NodeJS, Raspberry Pi
                .projectCard(style="background-image:url('/Images/xylo.jpg')")
                    .projectText
                        h1 Electronic Xylophone
                        br
                        p.
                            A system that is designed to teach beginners how to use a xylophone. 
                            An array of momentary switches  correspond  to a note on the xylophone. 
                            LCD displays the note played by the user.
                        p(style="color:red") Tools Used: Arduino
                .projectCard(style="background-image:url('/Images/gym.jpg')")
                    .projectText
                        h1 Gym Services Management
                        br
                        p.
                            Web application for managing gym services.
                            Users can login and book various services provided by the gym.
                        p(style="color:red") Tools Used: HTML, CSS, JS
                .projectCard(style="background-image:url('/Images/os.jpg')")
                    .projectText
                        h1 OS Algorithms Simulations
                        br
                        p.
                            Web application that displays interactive simulations for Operating Systems algorithms.
                            Simulations include Job Scheduling, Memory Page Replacement, Round Robin, etc.
                        p(style="color:red") Tools Used: NodeJS, HTML, CSS, JS

                .projectCard(style="background-image:url('/Images/plane.jpg')")
                    .projectText
                        h1 Airline Management System
                        br
                        p.
                            Web application for airline management <br>
                            The backend is managed by a Flask server. SQLite database with seven entities manages the entire airline system
                        p(style="color:red") Tools Used: Flask, HTML, CSS, JS

